# NBA Playoffs Prediction App

A single-page web application for predicting the NBA champion with a beautiful dark theme and neon accents.

## Features

- **One Prediction Per User**: Users can submit only one prediction, stored in localStorage
- **Voting Window Control**: Admin-controlled voting period via Google Sheets
- **Real-time Countdown**: Live countdown timer to voting deadline
- **Creative Team Selector**: Grid-based team selection UI
- **Responsive Design**: Mobile-first design with dark navy background and neon orange accents

## Setup

1. Deploy the HTML/CSS/JS files to Vercel
2. Set up Google Apps Script Web App with the following endpoints:
   - `?action=getConfig` - Returns `{votingOpen: boolean, deadline: "ISO string"}`
   - `?action=submitPick` - Accepts POST JSON `{name, pick, timestamp, userAgent}`
   - `?action=getLeaderboard` - Returns array of leaderboard entries

3. Update the `API_BASE` constant in `assets/predict.js` and `assets/leaderboard.js` with your Apps Script URL

## Google Sheets Configuration

Create a config tab with:
- Cell A1: VOTING_OPEN (TRUE/FALSE)
- Cell B1: VOTING_DEADLINE (ISO timestamp, e.g., 2025-06-01T23:59:00Z)

## Files

- `index.html` - Main prediction app
- `leaderboard.html` - Leaderboard page
- `assets/style.css` - Styling with dark theme
- `assets/predict.js` - Prediction logic
- `assets/leaderboard.js` - Leaderboard logic

## Fonts

- Bebas Neue for headings
- Inter for body text

## Colors

- Background: #0a0f1e (deep navy)
- Accent: #FF6B35 (neon orange)
- Text: #ffffff (white)
